so in death,

287
00:20:16,279 --> 00:20:17,519
you can make a contribution to Cang Feng.

288
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,319
Brother Jie.

289
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,000
Brother Jie.

290
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:20,240
Brother Jie, don't, don't.

291
00:20:20,519 --> 00:20:21,680
You can't do this to Wei Hao.

292
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:24,359
For the sake of our childhood...

293
00:20:24,839 --> 00:20:25,359
No.

294
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,319
For the sake of Madam.

295
00:20:28,079 --> 00:20:30,640
Do it to build good karma for Madam, Brother Jie.

296
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:33,599
I beg you, Brother Jie.

297
00:20:34,039 --> 00:20:35,559
You can't do this to me.

298
00:20:35,839 --> 00:20:36,440
Brother Jie.

299
00:20:37,119 --> 00:20:38,000
Brother Jie.

300
00:21:05,359 --> 00:21:05,920
Are you okay?

301
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:08,440
I'm fine.

302
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:16,799
It hurts.

303
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:21,680
So you still know pain?

304
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:29,680
Boss.

305
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:30,799
The Elders are here.

306
00:21:31,599 --> 00:21:32,160
I guessed as much.

307
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:35,920
You rest well first.

308
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:40,599
Will anything happen?

309
00:21:43,279 --> 00:21:43,799
It won't.

310
00:21:44,279 --> 00:21:44,759
It's fine.

311
00:21:46,559 --> 00:21:47,480
No matter what happens,

312
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:48,559
lock the door and don't come out.

313
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:50,480
I'll be right back.

314
00:21:52,839 --> 00:21:53,319
Wait for me.

315
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:13,920
Sister Jiali said

316
00:22:14,079 --> 00:22:15,559
you're abusing your power while Uncle Kun is away,

317
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:17,720
and got a few Elders to uphold justice for Wei Hao.

318
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:19,440
She also wants Madam to pay with her life.

319
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,039
They have already surrounded

320
00:22:21,039 --> 00:22:21,880
the entire villa.

321
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:25,480
You'd better be careful.

322
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,000
No need.

323
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:32,359
We must be cautious with the votes this time.

324
00:22:50,359 --> 00:22:52,079
Asking me to donate thirty million to him

325
00:22:52,519 --> 00:22:54,319
just to get the councilor's vote,

326
00:22:55,799 --> 00:22:57,920
just to become an insider.

327
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:01,640
He's really asking for a fortune.

328
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,079
Most of it

329
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,720
probably went to that little vixen.

330
00:23:09,839 --> 00:23:10,440
By the way,

331
00:23:11,759 --> 00:23:13,319
the phone has been ringing non-stop.

332
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:14,680
Is there anything urgent?

333
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,319
Something happened with Wei Hao.

334
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:17,559
It involves Hao Yu.

335
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:19,359
He can't get anything right,

336
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,039
but he ruins everything.

337
00:23:21,839 --> 00:23:23,480
Jiali called several times but couldn't find you,

338
00:23:23,559 --> 00:23:25,200
so she sent a few Elders to Zhijie's place.

339
00:23:25,519 --> 00:23:26,440
They brought a lot of people too.

340
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,680
Do you think you should return the call?

341
00:23:29,119 --> 00:23:30,880
Or make a trip over there?

342
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,400
The weather is bad.

343
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:38,559
The boat ride back would be very bumpy.

344
00:23:39,079 --> 00:23:40,160
Let's talk about it at dawn.

345
00:24:08,559 --> 00:24:10,880
You should be lenient when possible.

346
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:13,359
Let Wei Hao go first.

347
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,359
Wait for Ah Kun to return.

348
00:24:16,519 --> 00:24:17,400
Then we'll make a decision.

349
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:21,559
Wei Hao touched drugs and crossed the gang's line.

350
00:24:22,440 --> 00:24:23,400
He also embezzled funds.

351
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:25,680
He colluded with the police to sell out Cang Feng.

352
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,119
He was caught red-handed.

353
00:24:28,599 --> 00:24:29,759
Don't give me that.

354
00:24:30,519 --> 00:24:32,519
This is clearly the work of your femme fatale.

355
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:33,839
It's a setup by Hao Yu.

356
00:24:36,079 --> 00:24:37,759
Hao Yu almost got killed last time.

357
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:40,000
And this time she risked death to protect Cang Feng's data.

358
00:24:40,599 --> 00:24:42,480
Just because Wei Hao is your nephew...

359
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:44,480
And did some shady business for you...

360
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,119
Ji Zhijie.

361
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:47,720
You are too insolent.

362
00:24:49,519 --> 00:24:50,359
Your villa...

363
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:52,720
Has been surrounded by the Third Elder.

364
00:24:54,039 --> 00:24:55,039
If you don't...

365
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:57,240
Release Wei Hao today...

366
00:24:58,880 --> 00:25:01,319
I don't care about your Hao Yu or whatever.

367
00:25:02,559 --> 00:25:04,279
You won't walk out of here alive.

368
00:25:21,279 --> 00:25:23,200
Elders, you are abusing your seniority.

369
00:25:24,519 --> 00:25:25,599
I cannot obey.

370
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:27,759
Fine.

371
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:30,920
Then don't blame me.

372
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:37,519
Second Brother.

373
00:25:38,359 --> 00:25:39,440
I'll take my men and leave first.

374
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,359
As for the Xingzhou Port casino...

375
00:25:41,559 --> 00:25:43,480
We still need Zhijie's support.

376
00:25:45,519 --> 00:25:46,039
Retreat.

377
00:25:46,519 --> 00:25:47,000
Let's go.

378
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:47,680
You...

379
00:25:55,480 --> 00:25:58,079
Grandpa, there are many uncles at home.

380
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,480
What's going on?

381
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:09,119
No wonder Ah Kun values you so much.

382
00:26:10,519 --> 00:26:11,319
It turns out you...

383
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:14,119
Predicted we would come today.

384
00:26:14,319 --> 00:26:16,079
And made preparations in advance.

385
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,319
You're wrong, Second Elder.

386
00:26:19,559 --> 00:26:21,920
I am prepared at every moment.

387
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:27,440
You and Third Elder needn't worry about Wei Hao being gone.

388
00:26:27,559 --> 00:26:28,799
Those small businesses of yours...

389
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:30,039
Won't lack support.

390
00:26:33,039 --> 00:26:35,119
The legal venues at Xingzhou Port...

391
00:26:37,119 --> 00:26:38,920
I can partner with you on them.

392
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,559
Since it has come to this...

393
00:26:50,359 --> 00:26:51,759
I have nothing to say.

394
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:57,039
I know nothing about today.

395
00:26:58,039 --> 00:27:00,400
We never met today.

396
00:27:03,359 --> 00:27:03,839
Retreat.

397
00:27:15,279 --> 00:27:15,759
Fei Long.

398
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,400
It's not that we won't kill these old foxes.

399
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:20,680
We'll just deal with them another day.

400
00:27:21,519 --> 00:27:23,200
Find out who let them in today.

401
00:27:24,519 --> 00:27:25,160
Investigate it.

402
00:27:26,039 --> 00:27:26,680
And take them out.

403
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:35,079
Madam is still sick and can't be frightened.

404
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:13,279
I heard everything just now.

405
00:28:14,519 --> 00:28:15,319
They said...

406
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:17,519
They want me...

407
00:28:22,759 --> 00:28:24,119
Those disobedient guys...

408
00:28:24,119 --> 00:28:25,240
Were too loud.

409
00:28:26,519 --> 00:28:27,400
It's okay, Hao Yu.

410
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:34,000
Hao Yu.

411
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:37,759
I can give you everything you want.

412
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:41,559
Those who want to hurt you or have hurt you...

413
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:43,599
I won't spare them.

414
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,279
But what you shouldn't do...

415
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:52,640
You must not do at all.

416
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:40,000
See her true colors clearly!

417
00:30:40,279 --> 00:30:41,640
She's a cop's goddaughter!

418
00:30:41,839 --> 00:30:43,240
She's conspiring against you!

419
00:30:49,279 --> 00:30:49,680
I...

420
00:30:49,759 --> 00:30:50,319
Shut up!

421
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,119
You made Wei Hao mistakenly believe...

422
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:53,400
That Zhu Shuyi is you.

423
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,960
You arranged all of this.

424
00:30:55,119 --> 00:30:56,079
You planned it!

425
00:30:57,279 --> 00:30:58,440
Don't let this Witch go!

426
00:30:58,799 --> 00:31:00,160
She set us up again!

427
00:31:01,359 --> 00:31:02,039
I didn't!

428
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:04,400
I didn't!

429
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:08,839
Every single thing is related to you.

430
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:11,240
But also seems unrelated to you.

431
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:12,759
Tell me...

432
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:14,880
What should I do with you?
